{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5384219322","title":"关于一些问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":true,"dates":[{"id":"acc3c9d021","index":1,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":null,"articleId":"5384219322","article":{}},{"id":"ea57e61cdc","index":0,"year":1951,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"5384219322","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"114fee7702","type":"title","text":"关于一些问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"47441b9be5","type":"paragraph","text":"把劳动力组织在“变工队”、“扎工队”、“换工队”......等这一类的农村劳动互助组织里，有组织地进行耕种、锄草收割，这此单独耕种省工，又能多打粮食。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"41525bb5cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五一年一月三日）","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7f7ec94fdd","type":"paragraph","text":"只有中国工业发展了，中国在经济上不依赖外国了，才能全部的真正的独立。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3f50e01abf","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五一年七月）","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2c643ce567","type":"paragraph","text":"没有农业社会化，就没有全部的巩固的社会主义，而欲农业社会化，必须发展以国有企业为主体的强大工业。人民民主专政的国家必须有步骤地解决这个国家工业化的问题。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"471c7e71e0","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五一年七月二十六日）","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7373a3161","type":"paragraph","text":"假如没有苏联的存在，假如没有反法西斯的第二次世界大战的胜利，假如没有打倒日本帝国主义，假如没有各新民主国家的出现。......那么，堆在我们头上的国际反动势力必定比现在不知要大多少倍，在这种情况下，我们能够胜利么？显然是不能的。","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e5d40b1fda","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五一年十月四日）同志们，我们现在要和许多旧社会出身的人合作了。我们要小心，要预防旧社会的坏习气钻到中国共产党身上来。","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ec5cfc178","type":"paragraph","text":"（《人民日报》一九五一年十二月三十日）","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"5384219322","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":49,"end":48}}}},"__N_SSG":true}